summary:
Welcome to Open Security Summit 2020 Thank you for your interest in Open Security Summit 2020 (OSS 2020).
The attendee general flow (attendee journey) is as follows;
Buy a ticket Remote participants should also register using EventBrite. Create personal participant page Find sessions that you are interested in by viewing the topic index, tracks view or just simply list working, user or product sessions. Register to attend a session. If you need any assistance you can reach us in Slack or find more details about how you can get help here.

Session slides About this session &ldquo;Per OWASP A04:2021 – Insecure Design:
&ldquo;&ldquo;Write unit and integration tests to validate that all critical flows are resistant to the threat model&rdquo;&rdquo;
But how to do it at scale and reusing test from different projects/organizations? Can we build a community around the problem?&rdquo;
https://github.com/BBVA/susto

Working Together to improve the industry The Summit is also supported by a number of partners, who dedicate countless hours before, during and after the Summit.
